Title: msigdb.hs.v7.1.SYM
Description: Gene expression signatures from the Molecular Signatures Database (v7.1) excluding KEGG gene sets. Signatures are represented using gene symbols.

Title: msigdb.hs.v7.1.EZID
Description: Gene expression signatures from the Molecular Signatures Database (v7.1) excluding KEGG gene sets. Signatures are represented using Entrez IDs.
